---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - PickMyAITools"
  description="Read our terms of service to understand the rules and guidelines for using PickMyAITools."
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        By accessing and using PickMyAITools, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Use of Content</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        All content on PickMyAITools, including articles, reviews, comparisons, and guides, is for informational purposes only. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our written permission.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Accuracy of Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, but we cannot guarantee the completeness or accuracy of all content. Information about AI tools, pricing, and features may change without notice.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Our website contains affiliate links. We may earn commissions when you make purchases through these links. This does not affect the price you pay or our editorial independence.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Our website contains links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of service of these external sites.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        PickMyAITools and its operators are not liable for any damages resulting from your use of our website or the information provided. Use our recommendations at your own discretion.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of our website after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        If you have questions about these terms, please contact us.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
